channel.title: Try to find a RSPS with
channel.description:
Hello there!!!!! :)
I am look for a specific rsps.. I have looked for days on the server downloads page but I just cant find them... LOL i have looked through soo much but I haven't looked through all of them because there is sooo much so i need your help!!
I am trying to look for a rsps that is 508 with the home, EDGEVILLE SHOPS IN EDGEVILLE PK POINT SHOPS IN EDGEVILLE But it has all like KBD, Jad, etc.... Umm, it has good working ::commands, Not many updates needed, Not many glitches in the game... AND the teleport tab has all like, CITY TELEPORT, etc..
If you can find anything like that that would BE SOOOOO AWESOME!!!! :) I would love you for ever <3 no homo if your a boy... Anyways yeaaaa, soooo, just pm me if you found anything like that, if you found something sorta like that, im down to check it out :)
Pceeeee, thx for ur time :)
